contentfulPagePressRelease.title: H.H. Sheikha Moza Meets President of Croatia

childMarkdownRemark.html:
Chairperson of Qatar Foundation for Education, Science and Community Development (QF) HH Sheikha Moza bint Nasser met at her office this morning with HE President of the Republic of Croatia Kolinda Grabar-Kitarovic.

They discussed the scope for cooperation between Qatar Foundation and the Republic of Croatia in a number of scientific, cultural, and humanitarian fields.

HE the President awarded Her Highness the Grand Order of Queen Jelena with Sash and Morning Star, which is the highest ranking order given by Croatia to non-heads of state.
